Simple, fast and full-featured SlackBuilds.org package manager written in Rust.

- Sync the local SlackBuilds repository via rsync or git
- Resolve and build package dependencies automatically
- Build, install, reinstall, and remove packages
- Upgrade installed SBo packages
- MD5 checksum verification for downloaded sources
- GPG signature verification for SBo scripts (15.0 branch)
- Blacklist support to exclude packages from upgrades
- Display package information, dependencies, and reverse dependencies
- Search packages in the repository
- List installed SBo packages with optional filter
- Display the SlackBuilds.org changelog
- Clean the build directory
- Lock file to prevent multiple simultaneous instances
- Color output support

